@bijart\_dauth:  
Casting an instant or sorcery with retrace from your graveyard will not trigger [Pyromancer Ascension](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyromancer Ascension)'s first ability if it's the only card with this name in your graveyard. That's because early in the process of casting, you have to move that card from the graveyard to the stack. Therefore, you never get to complete casting your spell with another card with the same name **being** in your graveyard.  

For the exact same reason, flashback won't reward you with quest counters, either.  

Read the rulings, at least.  

